Package: nn2poly
Title: Neural Network Weights transformation into Polynomial Coefficients
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pablo",
           family = "Morala",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pablo.morala@uc3m.es",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4109-2330"))
Description: This package implements a method that builds the coefficients of a polynomial regression that performs almost equivalently as a given neural network (densely connected). This is achieved using Taylor expansion at the activation functions.
